"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?4/62/5095/abstract/1\">",
"      Loughran TP Jr. Clonal diseases of large granular lymphocytes. Blood 1993; 82:1.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
